2001-05-28  Simon Leinen  <simon.leinen@switch.ch>

	* test/if-counters.pl:
	Use ifAlias rather than locIfDescr.  The advantages are that ifAlias
	is not Cisco-specific, and it is defined even on ATM subinterfaces on
	Ciscos.

